               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-101vb)
 -
                     Introduction (fols. 3ra-4vb)
 - Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols.
                     4vb-11rb)
 - Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols. 17va-20ra)
                     - Mangada samāy “Journey to Heaven” (fol. 20ra-20va)
 - Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat
                     ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 20va-26ra)
 - Homily
                     by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols.
                     43vb-50vb)
 - Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols.
                     50vb-53vb)
 
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
